      "content": "that makes sense. i guess i was wondering about option B though. it mentions \"cultural heritage\" and a \"vibrant food scene,\" which sounds pretty sophisticated to me. why wouldn't that count as being \"culturally refined\" in a luxury context? isn't there a huge market for people who want that kind of high-end, worldly experience?",
